snippet.textDisplay:
^THIS is the lesson to be learned from listening to all of these tracks. There is art WITHIN the art. Video Games are hosts for visual and sound components that, even by themselves, can stand alone as pieces of art.

It really shows the true depth of the medium, and why video games can be so immersive at times.
